Zielauswahl & Scoring

As a user, I want to input my travel preferences so I get suitable destination recommendations.
As a user, I want each destination to have a score that shows how well it matches my preferences.
As a user, I want to see a sorted list of destinations based on their score.

Ergebnisübersicht

As a user, I want to see an overview of all matching destinations with key information.
As a user, I want to see the expected weather for each destination.
As a user, I want to see the estimated total travel costs for each destination.

Kartenansicht

As a user, I want to view all destinations on an interactive world map.
As a user, I want to select a destination by clicking on it on the map.

KI-Unterstützung

As a user, I want to ask an AI questions about a destination.
As a user, I want the AI to give me additional destination recommendations.

Detailseite

As a user, I want to see detailed information about a destination.
As a user, I want to see activities, tours, and sights available at the destination.
As a user, I want to access photos and external resources about the destination.
As a user, I want to see seasonal and weather-specific information for the destination.
As a user, I want to see a full price breakdown including travel, accommodation, and local costs.
As a user, I want to see travel warnings for my destination.
As a user, I want to be linked to official travel advisories.

Budget & Preisfunktionen

As a user, I want the system to automatically calculate the total travel costs.
As a user, I want to use a currency converter for destinations outside the Eurozone.
As a user, I want to compare all price-related factors between destinations.

Allgemeiner Mehrwert

As a user, I want all travel-relevant information (map, prices, weather, activities) in one dashboard.
As a user, I want to quickly compare multiple destinations side by side.
